            "body": "This seems to fix the problem:\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/move.c b/src/nvim/move.c\r\nindex dd9737ede..dcafdd607 100644\r\n--- a/src/nvim/move.c\r\n+++ b/src/nvim/move.c\r\n@@ -2455,6 +2455,7 @@ int onepage(Direction dir, long count)\r\n           if (curwin->w_topfill == loff.fill) {\r\n             curwin->w_topline--;\r\n             curwin->w_topfill = 0;\r\n+            curwin->w_valid &= ~VALID_CROW;\r\n           }\r\n           comp_botline(curwin);\r\n           curwin->w_cursor.lnum = curwin->w_botline - 1;\r\n```",
